#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/gather.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/gather.md:4
msgid ""
"简介：对`src`tensor沿`axis`维度按照`index`执行gather操作，gather操作含义见下图:\n"
"![image](./gather.png)\n"
"原型：\n"
msgstr ""
"Introduction: Perform a gather operation on the `src` tensor along the `axis` dimension according to `index`. The meaning of the gather operation is shown in the figure below:\n"
"![image](./gather.png)\n"
"Prototype:\n"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/gather.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.gather(\n"
" src: tensor,\n"
" index: tensor,\n"
" axis: int,\n"
" _semantic=None\n"
")\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/gather.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/gather.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/gather.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                | 说明                                                             |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `src`        | `tensor`          |  被执行gather操作的tensor                               |\n"
"| `index`     | `tensor`    | 需要gather的索引 |\n"
"| `axis`     | `int`    | 需要执行gather操作的维度 |\n"
"| `_semantic`   | -                 | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用|\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type      | Description                                                |\n"
"| ------------- | --------- | ---------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `src`         | `tensor`  | The tensor on which the gather operation is performed      |\n"
"| `index`       | `tensor`  | The indices to gather                                      |\n"
"| `axis`        | `int`     | The dimension along which to perform the gather operation  |\n"
"| `_semantic`   | -         | Reserved parameter, currently not supported for external calls |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/gather.md:14
msgid "返回值：`tensor`： gather后的结果"
msgstr "Return value: `tensor`: the result after gather"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/gather.md:16
msgid "### 2.2 支持规格"
